item.title: My Current Foundation Routine
item.description:
My Current Foundation Routine
Every year, I like to try out a new foundation application technique, but this technique was something I discovered by accident. I went on a quick trip to NY and forgot my foundation brush, so I decided to use my blush brush and surprisingly it worked better than I thought! I find myself applying foundation faster with this technique. Hair tutorial here http://bit.ly/FoundationHairTutorial Dry brushing isn't something that exists in the makeup world, it's from the art world.
